# File and Directory Structure
- src/config/ for configuration and settings
- src/core/ for framework base classes
- src/pages/ for page objects
- src/api/ for API clients
- src/utils/ for utilities and helpers
- tests/ui/ for UI tests
- tests/api/ for API tests
- tests/conftest.py for pytest fixtures
- Naming: files snake_case.py, classes PascalCase, functions and methods snake_case, constants UPPER_SNAKE_CASE.